Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说我认为作为你这个行业的人 你可能会理解 Imean I think as someone in your profession,you could probably understand..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们做了这个采访 但是没有人看到 that if wedid this interview and no one saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那么噗这就不重要了 then, poof, it doesn't matter.
