Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来重振萎靡不振的公众兴趣 .to revitalize flagging public interest..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是那些穿得像莎莉的变装英雄 ...the fad of costumed heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,公众对他们的一时狂热最终也会消退 …would eventually fade, even the ones dressed like Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,经过一番考虑我建议他们在公报上刊登一个大广告 After some consideration I suggested they take a large ad out in the Gazette..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请求更多的神秘人站出来 asking for more mystery men to come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是民兵组织的由来 Andthat's howtheMinutemen came tobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你第一次见到笑匠 CULPEPER: Now, when you first met The Comedian..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,夜枭、剪影和其他人时 .Nite Owl, Silhouette and the others..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么想的？ 你害怕吗？ …what were your thoughts? Were you intimidated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有一种解脱的感觉吗？ Was there a sense of relief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不说那是一段令人无比振奋的时光 Oh, it was an incredibly exhilarating time, I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们找到了一个 I think we all felt like we were partof a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都觉得自己是这个家庭的一部分 ..that we had found sort of a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们觉得自己是有价值的地方 where we could feel like we actually were of value.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都给民兵组织带来了不同的东西 Everyone brought something different to the Minutemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知何故 当我们在一起的时候我们都相信自己在做的事情 But somehow when we were together there was a bonding feeling..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我们产生了一种亲密感 …that we all believed in what we were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我说 “解脱”的原因是 Now, the reason I say "relief" is because many ofthe people back in those days..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候许多人认为你们都是很奇怪的、不正常的人 thought that you were all rather bizarre, abnormal individuals..
