Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为还有一些人只不过是罪犯 I think there are others that are nothing more than criminals…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,以此为手段 .who used this as a means..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为他们的暴力倾向辩护 ..to justify their violent tendencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一构成真正威胁的蒙面英雄 The only masked heroes that pose an actual threat..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是少数真的相信自己在做好事的 …aretherelatively fewborderline sociopaths..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,边缘反社会者 .that actually believe that they are doing good
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在面罩之下 Beneaththatmask..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就像你和我 .….they're just like you and me..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,充满希望、谷 欲望、恐惧 with hopes and desires, fears...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还有爱 ...love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望有一天 I hope that one day.….
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以对其中一位蒙面英雄进行心理分析 .I can psychoanalyze one of these masked heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那将是一件了不起的事 That would be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说这似乎是一个过去的时代 It seems a bygone era to us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,咆哮的40年代令人振奋的日子 The heady days of the roaring '40s.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人们渴望消遣 渴望戏剧 People were eager fordistraction, hungry for a fix of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么比一群自己设计的超级英雄 What better than a group of self-designed superheroes..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,表演一出夸张的街头打击犯罪的戏剧更棒的呢？ …to act out an exaggerated street theater of crime fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个超级恶棍横行的世界里 And in a world populated by supervillains..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢？ ..why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有臭名昭著的神秘主义者摩洛克 There was the notorious Moloch the Mystic..
