Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,当然后来出现了像大块头这样的现代超级反派 nLry.Full of beatu Americ De  membets ol the evident everywhere acroas good thatcruhed theJokhater re that zo may of u call home Ministe
